channel.title: SML can not launch the game
channel.description:
Hey,
i got an error on starting the game with SML; without SML ist normal working.
![Unbenannt|404x176](upload://4X0PD9yizbGBoQM9QQu00ogGhaY.png)
Testing Satisfactory of datafiles has no effect; SML reinstallation has also no effect on the Problem. The Problem is since updating five mods, deinstallation of the mods doesn't solve the problem with starting the game via SML.
Pleas help and thank you in advance! :slight_smile:

item.title: SML can not launch the game
item.dc:creator: @Judge_Stadalnikas Judge Stadalnikas
item.description:
@Judge_Stadalnikas wrote:

I’ve been getting this same issue after the new mod update, and just reverted back 2 updates, and the game loaded up fine, but only leaves you with the basic one door elevator. It’s a quick temporary fix.
